        <p class="lede-p"><strong>Grammarly is the best real-time writing assistant money can buy.</strong> It is also not an SEO tool, not a content optimizer, and not a publishing platform. After 30 days of testing every tier — plus interviews with 12 paying teams — here is the honest 2026 verdict, who genuinely benefits, and what to pair Grammarly with if your job involves growing organic traffic.</p>

