        </div>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">theStacc vs Grammarly — different problems, different tools</h2>
        <p>We wrote this review. We don't compete directly — Grammarly is an editor, theStacc is a publishing platform. But the budget question often comes up, so here's the side-by-side.</p>

