            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td>Free / $12/mo</td><td class="cell-yes">$99/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Real-time grammar + spelling</td><td class="cell-yes">Best-in-class</td><td>N/A — not an editor</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Tone + clarity suggestions</td><td class="cell-yes">Yes</td><td>Built into our briefs</td></tr>
              <tr><td>SEO research + keyword targeting</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">Included</td></tr>
