          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ The execution math</div>
          <p>Grammarly is rarely the budget problem — it's the writers and the SEO research stack that add up. Most teams spend $4,000+/mo on the full pipeline and forget Grammarly Premium is the cheapest line item on the spreadsheet. Keep it. Cut the other costs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta dark">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Wondering if your writing stack is too expensive?</h4>
            <p>We'll audit your current tooling + headcount and show you exactly what to keep, cut, or replace to get the same output for 1/10th the cost.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
