              <li>Useless on its own if your goal is organic rankings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Keep Grammarly. Outsource the SEO grind.</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles audits, content, publishing, GBP, and rank tracking — without you ever opening another dashboard. <strong>Try it for $1</strong>, cancel anytime.</p>
          </div>
