            <a href="/checkout/" class="cta-btn-inline">Start $1 trial <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No annual contract</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — how Grammarly stacks up</h2>
        <p>Grammarly's accuracy on grammar and spelling is the highest in the category. Where it loses ground is on long-form analysis and SEO awareness — neither of which is its job.</p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-cell">
            <div class="stat-num">30M+</div>
