        <h3>Grammar issue catch rate vs competitors</h3>

        <div class="chart-card">
          <div class="chart-head">
            <div>
              <div class="chart-title">Grammar issue catch rate (% · 2026 head-to-head test)</div>
              <div class="chart-sub">200-document test set covering grammar, clarity, style, and tone</div>
            </div>
            <div class="chart-legend">
              <span class="lg-1">Grammarly</span>
