        <p>Grammarly Premium wins on raw accuracy. ProWritingAid edges it on long-form fiction analysis. LanguageTool is the best free alternative. Hemingway is a style-only tool, so the catch rate is by design.</p>

        <blockquote class="pull">
          "Grammarly Premium is the single best $12/mo I spend on my business. It's like having a junior editor on every email I send. But if anyone tells you it'll help your SEO, they're selling something."
          <cite>— Marketing director, 50-person SaaS</cite>
