        <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Grammarly is best for — and who should skip</h2>

        <h3>Strong fit</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Anyone who writes for work — emails, docs, slides, decks</li>
          <li>Copywriters, content marketers, journalists (paired with SEO tools)</li>
